title: Diamond 3 Recruiting for a new competitive team : High Plat to Diamond+
body:
Hello, I would like to make a team for competitive play. Alternatively I'm joining one.

Let me know if you're interested and what role you play. Discord is preferred over skype. 

I can do any role except support. Here's my profile. http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=leonfresh

replies.body: Yo Leon, im looking to join a new team, im the jungler in the team youve been playing with(i think we played a few together) but im not playing with them anymore due to ceebs playing with a few of the tox players in it. Can fill any spot cept mid.
jg main would be interested, currently d5
